  "texts": [
    "Each modality presents unique integration challenges that require tailored approaches, highlighting the need for further research and development in this area.",
    "Representation Learning in Multimodal ContextsResearch in representation learning for multimodal contexts emphasized the importance of developing robust neural architectures that could handle diverse data types.",
    "Transformer models adapted for image-text interactions were particularly noteworthy, as they facilitated better cross-modal understanding [13], [22].",
    "Efforts to create unified representation spaces for text and images demonstrated substantial progress, although challenges remained in dealing with high-dimensional data efficiently [3], [23], [24].",
    "Audio-visual models improved significantly, particularly in tasks such as speech recognition and emotion detection [25], [26]."
  ],
